	Enron Capital & Trade Resources Corp.
	
	From:  "Pergher, Gunther" <Gunther.Pergher@dowjones.com>                      
     08/16/2000 08:16 AM
	

To: "Leopold, Jason" <Jason.Leopold@dowjones.com>
