X-From: Mona L Petrochko
X-To: Edward Hamb, James M Wood, Greg Cordell, Chris Hendrix, Martin Wenzel, Douglas Condon, Harry Kingerski, David Parquet@ECT, Tim Belden@ECT, Robert Badeer@ECT, Mary Hain@Enron, Roger Yang, Dennis Benevides
